  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Give the Gift of Education: Sponsor a Child Zambia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">More than a quarter of a million children in Zambia are not enrolled in school. We provide children in Livingstone, who wouldn&apos;t otherwise have it, with the opportunity to go to school. The sponsorship money pays school fees for a year, a set of uniform and shoes, a school bag, stationary, exercise books, and necessary text books. In addition, 29.5% of the sponsorship fee goes into a fund to improve the quality of education for all students at the school, both now and in the future.</narrative>
  </description>
